trans-unit.source: The SubMenuStyleCollection class is used to store and manage a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle> objects in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control.
trans-unit.target: A classe SubMenuStyleCollection é usada para armazenar e gerenciar uma coleção de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>objetos em um <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>controle.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.SubMenuStyle>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu> control uses the SubMenuStyleCollection class as the underlying data type of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>controle usa a classe de SubMenuStyleCollection como o tipo de dados subjacente a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>propriedade.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property provides additional style choices in addition to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuStyle%2A> and <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DynamicMenuStyle%2A> properties.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>propriedade fornece opções de estilo adicionais além de <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuStyle%2A>e <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DynamicMenuStyle%2A>Propriedades.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.DynamicMenuStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.StaticMenuStyle%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>

trans-unit.source: The first style in the SubMenuStyleCollection collection corresponds to the submenu style for the first level of the menu.
trans-unit.target: O primeiro estilo na coleção SubMenuStyleCollection corresponde ao estilo submenu para o primeiro nível do menu.

trans-unit.source: The second style in the collection corresponds to the submenu style for the second level of the menu, and so on.
trans-unit.target: O segundo estilo na coleção corresponde ao estilo submenu para o segundo nível do menu e assim por diante.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A> property is most often used to generate a navigation menu, like a Web site map, where menu items at a certain level should have the same appearance, regardless of whether they have submenus.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>propriedade geralmente é usada para gerar um menu de navegação, como um mapa de site da Web, onde os itens de menu em um determinado nível devem ter a mesma aparência, independentemente de terem submenus.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Menu.LevelSubMenuStyles%2A>
